dct_title_s: Outline map of Van Buren County
dct_description_sm: Abstract: Digital scan of a map of Van Buren County, Michigan, from an 1895 atlas. Shows civil townships, sections, roads, and municipalities.
Notes: From: Illustrated atlas of Van Buren County, Michigan / compiled from official records and local inspections by the Kace Publishing Company. Racine, Wisconsin : Kace Publishing Company, 1895.
